# Git LFS — catalog dataset + embedding artifact + attribute heads (#090).
# These live under the storage root /data/ (un-ignored selectively in
# .gitignore) and are pulled by `just setup` (git lfs pull) so a fresh clone
# is seed-ready without an out-of-band Fashion200k download. CI does NOT pull
# LFS (it seeds with AVSA_EMBED_STUB=1) — keeps LFS bandwidth low.
data/fashion200k/** filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
data/embeddings/** filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
data/attribute_heads/** filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
